data.eml:eml: A review of the Tychobythinus algiricus species group from North Africa (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Pselaphinae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Sabella, Giorgio, Viglianisi, Fabio Massimo, D’Urso, Vera, Nouira, Said (2014): A review of the Tychobythinus algiricus species group from North Africa (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Pselaphinae). Zootaxa 3893 (4): 579-586, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3893.4.7
